metadata.name: Poetry of the female body
metadata.description:
Only a woman can convey her emotions and feelings with a gesture or a pose, putting all the pain or joy, tenderness or contempt into a certain movement or position of her body. Only a woman can convey poetry with her body.

That collection is about me and my personal archiv for me it has a special value

This is the 1/1 NFT in the collection.

Size: 1500 x 1000px
